{"type":"answer","id":116753,"parentType":"question","parentId":14287,"uid":23714,"contents":"俺昨天发的“科学乳”素材，封杀了“细颈瓶”还有其他词可以用。<br>\n<br>\n<blockquote>法国著名微生物学家巴斯德设计了“鹅颈瓶实验”，证明了食物的发酵和腐败由空气中的细菌引起。下图是实验中使用的仪器——鹅颈瓶（又称“曲颈瓶”）。可以看到，鹅颈瓶是一种歪脖子的细颈瓶。<br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190506112758/https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/63/Coldecygne.svg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190506112758/https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/63/Coldecygne.svg\" alt=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190506112758/https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/63/Coldecygne.svg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20160220054721/https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/45/Col_de_cygne.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20160220054721/https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/45/Col_de_cygne.png\" alt=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20160220054721/https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/45/Col_de_cygne.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></blockquote>","date":"2019-12-29","agreeCount":73,"discussionCount":10}